description: Our goal is the identification of more and more the missing proteins from cancer cell lines. This project focuses on the membrance proteins separated by the ultracentrifuge and the low abundant peptides enriched by the Proteominer Kit and the hydrophobic peptides extracted by the organic solvent Acetonitrile.
